highlights.description: Section on community engagement and how people who are involved are typically the same people showing up or initiatives are not as proactive or sometimes inclusive.
Peter says if we want more civic engagement we have to be truly inclusive as a community.
Beatriz shares how her experience of not being included in a group discussion.
It was assumed Beatriz was going to take care of the children at a community meeting.
Carrie talks about affordable housing and whether we do or don't really want affordable housing in our community.
